ComicInfo.Summary: The other Sharon, the Returners, and her group of older and newer generation Cylons return to the Cylon’s main base ship where she seeks answers to who she is. The base ship sends Raiders to attack Sharon’s ship, but she quickly gains control of the Raiders and enters the main base ship. Sharon is eventually separated from the Rreturners, who attempt to set explosives on the ship. Sharon enters the forbidden garden and discovers the seat of all her memories and meets with Stan, her oldest childhood friend, who tells her she is actually Sharon Prime, the real human Sharon.
